<p>The original XML DocBook format of the manual for the C core
can be obtained by <a href="download.html#dev">downloading the
latest development version</a>.</p>

<p>Documentation for the Python interface is also included in the
Python docstrings, so you can use <code>pydoc</code> or the built-in Python help facility
as well.</p>
